60 450 Td
(The characteristic polynomial) Tj
ET
1 1 1 RG
2 w
60 430 m 660 430 l S
BT
/F2 18 Tf
1 1 1 rg
60 370 Td
(A v = L v holds for some nonzero v exactly when) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 18 Tf
1 1 1 rg
60 306 Td
(        det\(A - L I\) = 0) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 18 Tf
1 1 1 rg
60 242 Td
(The left hand side is a degree n polynomial in L,) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 18 Tf
1 1 1 rg
60 210 Td
(called the characteristic polynomial of A.) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 18 Tf
1 1 1 rg
60 178 Td
(Its roots are precisely the eigenvalues of A.) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
